title: Beet Napoleons
summary: Beet Napoleons is a gluten free, primal, and vegetarian main course. This recipe serves 2 and costs $5.36 per serving. One portion of this dish contains around 25g of protein, 38g of fat, and a total of 529 calories. 1 person found this recipe to be tasty and satisfying. If you have goat cheese log, olive oil, pepper, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. To use up the olive oil you could follow this main course with the Sauteed Banana, Granolan and Yogurt Parfait as a dessert. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes around 45 minutes. With a spoonacular score of 62%, this dish is solid. Similar recipes include Beet Napoleons, Beet And Goat Cheese Napoleons, and Beet and Goat Cheese Napoleons.
